tinymce-upload-alert-error-uploading-to-: I'm sorry, there seems to be a problem accessing the wiki from this dialogue. If the problem persists, try logging off and on again
tinymce-upload-confirm-file-already-exis:
The source file name already exists on the wiki or the source is a duplicate of a file on the wiki. Select one of the following actions:

  • overwrite to overwrite the existing file on the wiki
  • use to use the existing file on the wiki
  • rename to return to the dialogue and rename the source
